<h1 id="8-your-coolest-vim-airline">8. Your coolest vim-airline!</h1>
<p>And to finish today‚Äôs tips, nothing like inserting a cool <a href="https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Unicode">unicode</a> in your <a href="https://github.com/vim-airline/vim-airline">vim-airline</a>, add the symbol: ‚óâ  the section bar:</p>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-viml" data-lang="viml"><span class="k">let</span> <span class="nv">g:airline_section_z</span> <span class="p">=</span> <span class="s1">'‚óâ ‚ê§ % %l/%c'</span></code></pre></figure>

<p><img src="/assets/img/vim/bar-vim-airline.png" alt="Vim airline" /></p>

